<plot>Doctor Schneider has spent years in the medical profession; however, nothing can prepare him for the decision he must face when approached by Felicia, a longtime patient. In an attempt to help her elderly mother, Felicia asks the doctor for the unthinkable. With a lifetime of experience weighing on his conscience, Doctor Schneider is forced to consider anew the value of a human life. Set against the backdrop of World War II Germany, Doctor Schneider must finally come to terms with the horrors that exist outside his isolated walls.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?153615</url></doc>
